1. *Covek* je društveno biće. (Man is a social being.)
2. *Coveka* odlikuje inteligencija. (Intelligence characterizes man.)
3. *Coveku* je potrebno vreme da razvije sposobnosti. (Man needs time to develop abilities.)
4. *Covečanstvo* se trudi da postigne napredak. (Humanity strives to achieve progress.)
5. *Covečanstvu* je potrebna svest o zaštiti okoline. (Humanity needs awareness of environmental protection.)